        "tags": [
          "SERVICE_USER"
        ]
      },
      "date": "2013-01-16 17:02:36.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/d42b1874-5ffd-11e2-84d4-52540035b04c).  Ran 8 tests.  2 tests failed: sanityn, sanity.",
