      "date": "2013-01-18 10:15:09.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/2e2032ee-6155-11e2-b5e0-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
